parameters: Uwah... W-What's that... How can you wear something like that...

Isn't it a bit too early for swimsuits around here? We're being
watched, you know...?
Um, well... Is it really okay to wander around like that...?
Sister? It's rare to see you around here lately.

I sell food and travel essentials. There are also some rare items from
across the sea.

(If it's you... do you happen to know about Mr. Zato from
\c[6]Zato\c[0] who requested \n[2]?)

Um... Do you happen to know a merchant named Mr. Zato who is a
wholesaler?

Hmm, I've heard the name before, but I don't know the location. You
should try asking the general store owner, \c[6]Topos\c[0].
Thank you very much! I'll ask about it.

This city is prettier than Megista, isn't it? It used to be
just a fishing village about 50 years ago, but now it's a new city.

Would you like me to guide you? I know a restaurant with
delicious fish dishes.

Would you like me to guide you? I don't really recommend the beach
right now though.

Would you like me to guide you? I know a restaurant with delicious
fish dishes.

I came all the way from the southwestern kingdom of Eitna to make a
living in Megista. My intuition tells me there are still plenty of
treasures to be found.

……Is it normal to walk around naked in the Kingdom of Del? T-That can't
be true... right...?
……Whoa... Is that kind of fashion popular around here?
……Since it looks really cold, you should wear something.
……Whoa... Big boobs... That's a weird swimsuit...

It is said that the ruins within the territory of Melgius have been
completely excavated, but that is only within the range that people
can easily enter. There should still be unexplored ruins in more
dangerous places.

Perhaps... there might be something like the Drifting Ruins rumored to
exist.

This is the port town of Marusta. It's a city with many travelers, but
be careful not to get too carried away.

……Are you listening? Hm? I'm saying that there are limits even to being
open-minded.

……Are you listening? Hm? You can't dress like that in this kind of
traffic.
……Are you listening? Hm? At least go to the beach.

……Are you listening? Hm? You can't dress like that in this kind of
traffic.

We have to find Zato-san who has been taking care of Wize... For now,
should we ask someone who runs a shop around here?

(However... it's already late and there's no one around. \c[6]Let's
stay overnight\c[0] and ask around this area tomorrow.)
